            <div class="title">
                House Of Commons Rebuilding
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1943-10-28/debates/d900ea3e-1116-4b4a-9749-1eeb2015590e/WaterUndertakingsBillLords" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
